          <p>When you make an offering of good liquor, fresh fruit, or fresh-cooked meat and call up the shade of the skull, it manifests before you in shadows. The shade knows much about ancient times, the Green Lords, and their workings. It has no power, but can answer questions. Before it does, it will demand the right to "ride" you and experience the pleasures of living. Instinct: to fulfill its increasingly specific longings. While it rides you, the shade communicates only through impulse and desire. When it compels you to act against your wishes, mark XP if you comply. If you resist, you are Defying Danger.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
