          <p>On a rare dry spot in Ferrier's Fen, besieged by foulness, is an ancient arch that still — improbably — stands. The keystone remains clear, engraved with a sigil that makes the eyes water and that drives evil away. You can learn the secrets of the sanctifying mark, but to do so you must…</p>
