          <p>An exquisitely fine wool, dyed a pale blue-gray and embroidered with stylized clouds. The edge boasts blue-white runes stitched with aetherium wire. It feels damp, smells of rain and ozone, and flutters in a breeze that isn't there. When you don the cloak, you become aware of the presence bound within, thrumming and impatient. To unlock the mysteries of the cloak, you must…</p>
