          <p>Two bronze hand mirrors, identical in every way, etched around their edges with the same repeating pattern of interlocked knots. When you hold one up and look into it, you see not your own reflection but a grey, fog-filled void. The other mirror shows the same thing. To unlock their mysteries, you must…</p>
