            <label><input type="checkbox" name="attr_mn61_req1" value="1"> …pierce your own skin with the needle and pull a visible thread of light from the wound.</label>
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="attr_mn61_req2" value="1"> …sew the thread into something living (it need not be willing).</label>
