        <label class="arcana-unlock-label" for="mn62_unlocked">Unlocked</label>
        <div class="arcana-front">
          <p>A small clay pot, sealed with wax that has been stamped with a sigil you don't recognize. It smells faintly sweet even through the seal. Cracking the wax open and inhaling even briefly produces a sudden, sharp clarity — followed by a gap in memory lasting several minutes. To unlock its secrets, you must…</p>
